
#After downloading zookeeper and Kafaka use the below commands to run Zookeeper and kafka server inside windows folder
Below is the url where i have downloaded Kafka and zookeepr

https://kafka.apache.org/quickstart

// kafka commands///

running the zookeeper after going inside bin/windows folder

zookeeper-server-start.bat ..\..\config\zookeeper.properties.


running the kafka server which internally start the broker

kafka-server-start.bat ..\..\config\server.properties.

Check the data present inside topic

kafka-console-consumer.bat --bootstrap-server localhost:9092 --topic your_topic_name --from-beginning
